<br>
Mala does FR, CR, MR, PR<br>
<br>
Malo does FR, CR, MR, DR<br>
<br>
So if you have people needing debuff for Disease spells (like shaman slow) then you should wait until slow lands before you overwrite that shamans Malo with Malosini. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Master Eandori Raintree<br>
